quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  31,1,ALIF LAM MIM
  31,2,These are the verses (revelations) of the Wise Book
  31,3,A guidance and a mercy to those who do good
  31,4,"Those who establish regular prayer and give charity, and who are sure of the Hereafter"
  31,5,"These are in true guidance from their Lord, and these are the Successful"
  31,6,"But amongst men are those who purchase (pay for) idle tales without knowledge (or meaning), to lead astray men from the path of Allah, and to make a jest of it; for them is shameful woe"
  31,7,"And when Our signs are recited to such a one, he turns away in arrogance as though he heard them not, as if there was deafness in both his ears. Announce to him a grievous penalty"
  31,8,"Verily, those who believe and do right, for them are Gardens of Bliss"
  31,9,"Wherein they will abide; it is a promise of Allah in truth, and He is the Mighty, the Wise"
  31,10,"He created the heavens without supports that you can see, and He placed upon the earth firm mountains lest it should shake with you; and He dispersed therein all kinds of beasts; and We send down from the heavens water, and We caused plants of every noble"
  31,11,"This is the Creation of Allah; show me that which others beside Him have created. Nay, the unjust are in obvious error"